<title>USA: Helmstar extends share buy-back program.</title>
<headline>Helmstar extends share buy-back program.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Helmstar Group Inc said Friday it would extend its share buy-back program for 12 months.</p>
<p>The program started June 10 last year and authorizes the company to buy back 1 million of its 5.5 million shares outstanding. So far, Helmstar has bought back 30,000 shares, a company statement said.</p>
